{"tid":599172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=？？工作問題困擾　60後燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-03-20T07:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T08:47:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eebf20c600b4fb1833343aee932b2358c9240033","tid":599172,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"油麻地男子酒店燒炭身亡。中午12時許，吳松街92號一間酒店，職員見一名男租客逾時仍未辦理退房手續，遂拍門查看，惟亦無回應，並聞到房內傳出炭味，立即報案。警方聯同消防人員到場進入房間，發現該男子昏迷房內，身旁有一堆炭灰，經檢驗證實明顯死亡，警方初步相信事件無可疑，正聯絡其親友處理後事。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息，死者年約50歲，本地人，留有遺書，疑因工作問題而萌死念。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180320/bkn-20180320132533150-0320_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180320%2Fbkn-20180320132533150-0320_00822_001.html&d=jg%2FN9Lazch%2FjdqJZ5K2jbE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1a74c5ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180320/bkn-20180320132533150-0320_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c9a4024915acb30615feeade8110667170b6f94d","tid":599172,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad662e22ca8b57bf3ddcfa05ed42b56e9ffca6c6","tid":599172,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9a4024915acb30615feeade8110667170b6f94d","tid":599172,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"687e0ce9a57777ed0c26a0065256ce7c8f924064","tid":599172,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad662e22ca8b57bf3ddcfa05ed42b56e9ffca6c6","tid":599172,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9a4024915acb30615feeade8110667170b6f94d","tid":599172,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20